title: PS5 is Sold Out Everywhere - Kinda Funny Games Daily 11.23.20
description:
Blessing and Tim discuss PS5 selling out, The World Ends With You sequel, Cyberpunk 2077 being out in the wild, and more!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:03:55 - Housekeeping
No KFGD on Wednesday, Thursday, and Friday
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Tom Bock & Black Jack
The Roper Report   -

00:10:04 - What do you think this says about PlayStation’s PS5 release?  - Best Friends Q:James Halliday
00:18:30 - Cyberpunk 2077 Copies Appear to Be in the Wild - Adam Bankhurst @ IGN
00:25:55 - A new The World Ends With You game has been revealed - Tom Phillips @ Eurogamer
00:31:00 - There’s also a TWEWY anime incoming! - Jordan Oloman @ IGN
00:31:50 - Heads up: there’s an autosave bug in Watch Dogs Legion - Joe Skrebels @ IGN
00:33:30 - Does it fall to the consumers to research any possible bugs for any game they plan to purchase? - Best Friends Q:Wispa
00:41:20 - Bioware and Ubisoft veterans create Yellow Brick Games - Marie Dealessandri @ GiBiz
00:45:40 - Out today
00:39:20 -  Ad  
 Reader mail   -
